content: borisudovicic: Demonstrated a strong focus on strategic planning and future development by creating 40 issues, including detailed plans for "Provide an option for webhooks (Farcaster)" and "Update Neynar SDK (Farcaster)," alongside a comprehensive set of issues outlining improvements across documentation, developer experience, and core system enhancements. They also addressed immediate concerns by closing two issues related to "One run action chain history" and "Custom Plugin Schema migration issues."
